      "comment": "JUST A BABE (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Kia Keeping (34.48) in a Grade 6. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Can measure up this time. SECRETS WE KEEP (1) could manage only fourth at this track last time but impressed when posting a handy 37.71 over 643m at Gawler the start prior. Should be in this for a long way. OREGON JANET (4) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fourth (43.48) at this track. Has ability and can measure up. DISCO HOMER (8) cannot be underestimated.",
